  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220&deg;C/ 200&deg;C (fan)/ 425&deg;F/ Gas 7</p>\r\n<p>Cut the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into large, bite-sized pieces</p>\r\n<p>Strip the<strong> thyme leaves</strong> from the stalks and chop them finely</p>\r\n<p>Crush the <strong>garlic</strong> with the side of a knife, keeping the skins on&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> potatoes</strong>, <strong>chopped thyme</strong> and<strong> garlic</strong> to a baking tray with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 15-20 min (approx. step 6)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the&nbsp;<strong>dried cranberries</strong>&nbsp;finely</p>\r\n<p>Zest the<strong> orange<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong><span class=\"text-danger\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>chopped cranberries, orange zest</strong>, 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span>&nbsp;<strong>cold&nbsp;water</strong>&nbsp;and the juice of the <strong>orange<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> to a pot and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low and cook for 20-25 min or until the cranberries have broken down and the liquid has reduced &ndash; this is your <strong>cranberry sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile,&nbsp;cut the&nbsp;<strong>chicken breast<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>in half lengthways</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wrap the<strong> chicken</strong> in&nbsp;the&nbsp;<strong>bacon rashers</strong>&nbsp;tightly&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the&nbsp;<strong>bacon-wrapped chicken</strong>&nbsp;and cook for 3 min, turning occasionally until browned on all sides</p>\r\n<p>Tip: use a pair of tongs to roll the chicken so that the bacon stays nicely wrapped around it!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the<strong> Brussels sprouts</strong> into quarters</p>\r\n<p>Once&nbsp;the&nbsp;<strong>bacon-wrapped&nbsp;chicken</strong>&nbsp;is browned, transfer it to the baking tray with the&nbsp;<strong>potatoes</strong></p>\r\n<p>Return the tray to the oven for a further 5 min</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>Brussels sprouts</strong> for a final 10-15 min, or until everything's crispy and the chicken is cooked through&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/294.new.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>bacon-wrapped chicken</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Serve the <strong>chicken</strong> with the <strong>potatoes</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>sprouts&nbsp;</strong>and <strong>cranberry &amp; orange sauce</strong> to the side</p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
